54:41.543 --> 54:42.675
Walter, stop!

54:42.677 --> 54:43.712
Please.

54:44.913 --> 54:46.746
Stop! Please!

54:55.924 --> 54:57.960
What do you want from us, Addison?

54:59.828 --> 55:02.598
You want to know why my son was killed?

55:05.632 --> 55:07.402
I don't know why.

55:10.071 --> 55:13.609
But maybe we're just going to
have to learn to live with that.

55:20.514 --> 55:23.016
I'm so sorry.

55:23.018 --> 55:25.753
I'm so sorry. I didn't
mean to make it worse.

