- Yeah.

57:36.817 --> 57:39.686
I don't know. Maybe that's what Strauss
meant by "emotional difficulties."

57:39.688 --> 57:41.087
Phoebe.

57:41.089 --> 57:42.857
Uh, hey.

57:44.192 --> 57:47.694
I'm sorry, Mom. Just one second.

57:47.696 --> 57:49.862
- Addy, I gotta go. I...
- Wait. I just...

57:49.864 --> 57:51.300
Phoebe! Please.

57:53.734 --> 57:55.337
Addy, what is it?

57:58.706 --> 58:03.345
You know, I never told you what
happened that day with my mom.

58:05.013 --> 58:06.047
No.

58:09.250 --> 58:10.819
She was fine.

58:12.286 --> 58:15.621
Nothing was wrong with her.

58:15.623 --> 58:17.325
That morning, we were having breakfast,

58:17.558 --> 58:20.661
and then I went to school,
and when I came back she was...

58:23.031 --> 58:24.299
It's okay.

58:26.299 --> 58:31.003
She was still sitting in the
same seat where I left her.

58:31.005 --> 58:35.110
At the hospital, they told
us that she'd had an aneurysm.

58:37.578 --> 58:39.344
Then,

58:39.346 --> 58:42.848
last week, we see Kevin at the coffee shop.

58:42.850 --> 58:44.918
- He gave us our coffee.
- Addison.

