01:10:28.822 --> 01:10:31.590
<i>but they only give you
three-and-a-half inches.</i>

01:10:31.592 --> 01:10:33.160
<i>Three-and-a-half
inches on a page.</i>

01:10:33.392 --> 01:10:35.627
<i>I'm sorry, but my worst
