01:10:44.105 --> 01:10:45.703
<i>However,
how are you expected</i>

01:10:45.705 --> 01:10:47.905
<i>to express the very
essence of your being</i>

01:10:47.907 --> 01:10:50.810
<i>and your views on how
insanely crazy this world is</i>

01:10:50.812 --> 01:10:52.052
<i>in such a tiny space on a page?</i>

